  "caption": "Agent tool use isn't magic. It fails.Agents struggle with malformed inputs or unexpected tool outputs. They'll often retry, but without solid error handling, they can get stuck in loops or hallucinate. Real-world agents need explicit fallbacks and monitoring.Save this before shipping your next agent.Follow @byteflowlabs for AI systems, no hype.",
